{"tid":1395692,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"侵：9月1日起向價值3000億美元中國貨品徵收10%關稅","createTime":"2019-08-01T23:39:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T05:21:24.000Z","uid":13663,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"20140c4df81fb1f9d8a9bbb34e828c60fb7a9d7e","tid":1395692,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T23:39:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9450eda9e3677b1a4b17efddb5517b8c34473fe9","tid":1395692,"uid":13663,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T23:40:02.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普8月1日於Twitter留言，稱華府會在9月1日起向價值3000億美元中國貨品徵收10%關稅。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n特朗普於Twitter表示，貿易談判代表回國後指與中國在將來簽訂協議問題上有建設性對話，但他認為中國早應在3個月前與美國簽訂貿易協議，不過北京方面在簽約前卻決定重新談判。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，中國同意購買大量美國農產品，但沒有實現；再加上中國國家主席習近平曾說會阻止類鴉片止痛劑芬太尼（Fentanyl）出口到美國，不過至今仍沒做到，導致很多美國人喪生。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普稱，目前貿易談判仍在進行，因此在這段期間，美國在9月1日起會向中國價值3000億美元的貨品徵收10%關稅，這不包括本身已經面對25%關稅的2500億產品。他希望與中國就全面的貿易協議有正面對話，並覺得兩國會有光明的未來。"},{"pid":"7d8a1bfad861fc3f52a7b333bbcca126e6f30ad2","tid":1395692,"uid":288707,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T23:41:49.000Z","msg":"撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dae0ed903f85e1ccf5fe225483bc320bf7188567","tid":1395692,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T23:43:31.000Z","msg":"但係佢都講明香港嘅事自己處理返證明佢哋唔會插手所以唔會再相信鬼佬自己的事自己做"},{"pid":"5a06430061fb87845e834b9e326cf9f484616f8f","tid":1395692,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T23:44:35.000Z","msg":"Trump to Impose 10% Tariff on $300 Billion of Chinese Goods<br />\nBy VOA News<br />\nAugust 1, 2019 03:00 PM<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voanews.com/economy-business/trump-impose-10-tariff-300-billion-chinese-goods\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voanews.com%2Feconomy-business%2Ftrump-impose-10-tariff-300-billion-chinese-goods&d=oOhF4K9gmG%2F73F8T9h6VFOdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=1da3f45b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.voanews.com/economy-business/trump-impose-10-tariff-300-billion-chinese-goods</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7122501e6c79568aada394f149144b79ec65373","tid":1395692,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d8a1bfad861fc3f52a7b333bbcca126e6f30ad2","tid":1395692,"uid":288707,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T23:41:49.000Z","msg":"撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T23:45:35.000Z","msg":"話左架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d07242b1f9f530c97b5398c7b0f418bdbfd6b209","tid":1395692,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dae0ed903f85e1ccf5fe225483bc320bf7188567","tid":1395692,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T23:43:31.000Z","msg":"但係佢都講明香港嘅事自己處理返證明佢哋唔會插手所以唔會再相信鬼佬自己的事自己做"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T23:46:40.000Z","msg":"黎智英助手: 「特朗普」與「香港示威」可能係俾華爾街日報抹黑<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1394163\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1394163</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f66d729d50f5a0b4f0920c6e4fac25b74add0ad7","tid":1395692,"uid":263991,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T23:47:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">後果自負！後果自負！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d3831791f91bc5ed206157ba3f7c97ba4817c2e","tid":1395692,"uid":272592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9450eda9e3677b1a4b17efddb5517b8c34473fe9","tid":1395692,"uid":13663,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTim